Game: Grand Theft Auto V

Type: Physics / Collision

Title: Character clipping through environment during high-speed vehicle exit

Environment:

Platform: PC / Console
Mode: Open World Free Roam

Steps to Reproduce:

Drive a vehicle at high speed
Crash into a solid object (wall/barrier)
Immediately exit the vehicle

Expected Result:
Character exits vehicle safely without intersecting environment

Actual Result:
Character partially clips through ground or nearby object

Severity: Medium

Impact:
Breaks immersion and may lead to temporary gameplay disruption

Notes:
Occurs more frequently at higher speeds and tight collision spaces
